    "56997667": {
      "title": "How to Teach Writing",
      "abstract": "* An uncomplicated analysis of the nature of writing, particularly in terms of process, product and genre * Discussion of the practical implications of teaching the theory of writing * Descriptions of a broad spread of writing tasks, simple and extended, to help teachers select those that will be most effective in developing their students' writing skills"
